Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The history of games can be traced back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the way to Ancient Egypt 5,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These ancient games decided the fate of the citizens and the kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were called the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the time where a boy has solved the Millennium Puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and released the Dark Games has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy with both a heart of light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People refer to him as Yuugiou: The Game King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Terrifying\N Blue-Eyes White Dragon"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, it's your turn, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'cha doin' Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Duel Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so noisy, just shut up and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fighting game where you use Monster and Magic Cards against the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here I go! Battle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's two types of card positions, Attack and Defense. The first to hit 0 Life Points loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn now, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll attack with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use such a powerful card without even a hint of a warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost right out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, you're so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm powerful, it's just my grandpa's a serious game maniac. I get great cards from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We'll stop by Yugi's after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:03:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, maybe I'll convince him to show you his super-rare card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super-rare card? It couldn't be, could it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, everyone's together today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you show everyone your amazing card?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make an exception, since this is my most valuable possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called the Blue-Eyes White Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Super-Ultra-Rare Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's so special...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only four of these in the entire world! This card isn't even for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Can I hold the card, gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, come on! Then how about showing me some other strong cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could the heir of Kaiba Corporation want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Yugi-kun's grandpa was a card maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you play Duel Monsters, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came at the perfect time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be pals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks, I'd rather pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you guys are in my league.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one to win the Duel Monsters National Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we're at completely different levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say? Shut up and play me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, does a shop like this even have any decent cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is the legendary Blue-Eyes White Dragon in a dump like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe he has the real card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, if you give me that Blue-Eyes White Dragon, I'll trade you every single one of these cards in return!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't gonna trade it, I can buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Name your price!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me anything, and I can pay it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I'm not selling you this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't because it's such a strong card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because this card is a gift from my most precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I treasure this card just the same as I do that precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing you pay me could possibly measure up to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0} did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would feel the same even if it were a weak card, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card has the same heart as that precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cards have a heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a load of bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cards are power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just you see. I'll make sure to get that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-sama, we have obtained the 3 cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that just leaves that old geezer's card, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wel-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invite you to a Duel on behalf of Kaiba-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugoroku Mutou-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I were to refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we will use force.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That boy misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll teach him the heart of the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My god, Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're ya talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, we've come again to get more cards today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather careless of him to leave the door unlocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandfather is currently under my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you come pick him up at my office?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to show that boy the heart of the cards, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well aren't you slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! What did you do to Gramps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we did was Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bet was the other person's most treasured card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think he may have been a bit shocked by my Virtual Simulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have pulled some cheap tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prove it with the card I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my grandpa's most cherished card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only three cards of the same name are permitted in a deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fourth would be in the hands of an opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fourth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My Blue-Eyes White Dragon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-Yugi... take these...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These cards hold the heart I pit against him and lost miserably with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can beat that boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach that boy the true meaning of the heart of the cards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:09:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just leave you here, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want revenge for your grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave Gramps to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and teach him what the heart of the cards is all about, just like Gramps said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight him, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you're the one who changed a person like me who was obsessed with fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now put your hands out, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! This is the proof of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic marker ink will eventually fade away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but our hearts and our friendship will never disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, Honda and I will take Grandpa to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay and support Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of him, Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are the Kaiba Special Rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both have 2000 Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first one of us to hit 0 Life Points loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Virtual System, start up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, with my grandpa's soul hanging on the line, I will defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, begin the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use Cyclops to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster came to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Virtual Simulation System!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how he weakened Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack you with\N Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what in the-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desperate Fireball Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game isn't as interesting if the players don't play multiple Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use this card to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dark Clown?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, his Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize the Attack Points of Winged Dragon are 1400.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy only has 600 Attack Points, so he can't win in the way he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I add this card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Magic Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generator of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This triples the Attack Points of a {\1c&H000000&\1a&H00&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&}Dark{\r} Attribute Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saggi the Dark Clown, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Glide!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the destructive power of a Combo Attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This damn Kaiba knows the game inside and out...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But these cards were formed into a Deck by the heart of my grandfather, a game master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's got to be something useful in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This card can't beat the Dark Clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have to hold on and play another Monster in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Glide!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the same Card Deck made by that dying old geezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear his dying breath with each card you draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa lent me these cards because he believes in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}I can hear the burning, ambitious {\i1}soul{\i0} of my Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, do you hold that kind of belief in {\i1}your{\i0} cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in these cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I drew is Gaia the Dark Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding 2300 Attack Points, he attacks the Dark Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Shaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know the winner yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he tear up Gramp's card?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaia the Dark Knight is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get what I want, no matter {\i1}what{\i0} it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:15:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with two other Blue-Eyes hidden in my Deck, you can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Do you plan to keep using Defense Mode until you run out of cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew the second Blue-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just give in and admit defeat, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Swords of Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seals the attacks of all Monsters on your side of the field for 3 turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pointless action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could you possibly gain in just 3 turns?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like Kaiba said, I just have 3 useless Sealed Cards in my hand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I continue fighting with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}This isn't like you, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}Listen, there's nothing useless in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}Just like how you put so much effort into the Millennium Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}The Millennium Puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}Cards are just like solving the pieces to a puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}Like the pieces of a puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Exodia{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Exodia is in this Card Deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a myth in Duel Monsters that states when you gather the 5 needed cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you can exchange them for a much greater Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(0,700)}But no one has ever successfully done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and draw your card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fourth piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the same no matter what card you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play this Monster to attack your Defense Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judge Man, with 2200 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I put it in Defense Mode, it'll just get done in by Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll {\i1}attack{\i0} Judge Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judge Man is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not {\i1}nearly{\i0} enough to harm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one turn remaining until the seal is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I just drew is the third Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Yugi. Draw your {\i1}final{\i0} card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because next turn, I'll attack you with all {\i1}three{\i0} Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter {\i1}what{\i0} card you play, you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I was only able to Summon the legendary Exodia, I'd have a change of winning...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the chances of me actually getting the card I need in this last turn are close to zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The cards are getting further and further away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I'm just scared to draw the next card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The "Magic Circle"...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}This is the mark of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}Yugi, you aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(300,300)}We're all in this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be afraid anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find despair by reaching your hand out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just found hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I just drew...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is The Sealed One, Exodia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just gathered all 5 cards this very moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exodia, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just create a {\i1}miracle{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light of Hellfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exodo Flame!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yugi's win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother {\i1}lost{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now matter how strong a card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless if you can't connect your heart with that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you connect your heart with the cards, miracles happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could {\i1}I{\i0} lose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, your heart is being driven by evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind Crush!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just destroyed the evil within your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Pegasus, Seto Kaiba from Kaiba Corporation has been beaten in a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(252,232)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Jounouchi wants to play Duel Monsters seriously for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's grandfather is going to give him special lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That moment, Yugi receives a video tape in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the sender is... Pegasus Crawford.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really wants to play a game through the video?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? A Dark Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Illusionist No-Face's Trap
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:21:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:22:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
